* This interface represents the amount of space occupied by a three-dimensional * object or region of space, expressed in cubic units. The system unit for * this quantity is "m³" (cubic meter). Jean-Marie Dautelle 1.0, January 14, 2006
* Holds the SI unit (Système International d'Unités) for this quantity.
<declaration type="Unit" name="UNIT" />
